    tr: "wam<u>aa</u> yastawii <strong>a</strong>l-a'm<u>aa</u> wa<strong>a</strong>lba<u>sh</u>iiru wa<strong>a</strong>lla<u>dz</u>iina <u>aa</u>manuu wa'amiluu <strong>al</strong><u>shshaa</u>li<u>haa</u>ti wal<u>aa</u> <strong>a</strong>lmusii-u qaliilan m<u>aa</u> tata<u>dz</u>akkaruun<strong>a</strong>",
